Seagram Co Ltd's Joseph E. Seagram andSons Inc said it is realigning its Fine Wine operationsfollowing last week's sale of its medium-priced table winesbusiness.    Seagram Vintners, the entity under which all fine wineoperations were group, is being dissolved, the company said.The Seagram Classic Wine Co will move its operations to theWest Coast, the company said.    Seagram Chateau and Estate Wines Co will continue to beheadquartered in New York, the company said. Reuter&#3;